    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolutely wonderful to me. It\u2019s in great shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend trips. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, so it\u2019s ready for a new home and many more miles of memories. It drives smooth and looks fantastic\u2014you're going to love it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
