      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and let me tell you, it's been a total rockstar. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a smooth ride without any fuss. It\u2019s been well-cared for and is ready to hit the road with you today. Drop me a message if you're interested, I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 34500.0,
