    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive valve shim adjustment. The drivetrain utilizes the robust Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory limited-slip differential. Suspension dynamics are enhanced by a refreshed bushing kit and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the chassis retains its signature communicative feedback. While the finish exhibits minor road wear consistent with its mileage, the powertrain remains exceptionally tight with linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline. Recent service includes a cooling system refresh and a high-performance fluid flush.",
